Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭蟲們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌引來他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以將功贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞開身心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展露你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又舊地重遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:26.87,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(600,450)\pos(940,577)\shad0\bord2\be1}Last Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 這裏就是一切的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告稱2040年初次遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是11年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支第117次調查船團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功捕獲神秘生物Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並開始研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究者中也包括那位格蕾絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟用真名正大光明地混入Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 早發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第117調查船團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧·諾姆博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始文明研究第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蘭歌在「鳥之人」中扮演的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲馬 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論文的草稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於空間水晶與植入技術實現超時空網絡的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲·奧格娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了醫療記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪·美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘭歌的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪·美博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最初的V型感染癥患者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患病的母體懷胎並生下了蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是蘭歌她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是根據論文推測的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河規模的完全即時植入網絡概念圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把空間水晶作為植入體的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上在銀河兩端都不會產生延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為現實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為銀河規模的超並列思維網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想被人知道自己的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再偷偷想 「好男人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河統一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這理想聽來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也有貓膩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非完全的並列思維
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為結點的端子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對其他終端有優越性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把它們集約化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終的中央一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會相對於其他成為上位存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配銀河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有個很大的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能讓全部人類都植入化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此才需要Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗者只有死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受者成為下屬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易跨越斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連反應彈也奈何不了的Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類沒有對抗手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯一能與Vajra進行交流的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra網絡的粒子協議解析
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,92.3%完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真單純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算監聽Vajra之間的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始終難以解析的協議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦轉換成人的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能如此輕易被解析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的血會互相傷害 開始自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會證明我是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類會超越原始文明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把判明的事實傳送給了新統合政府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 通信延遲和議會表決…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠我們做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會跟我來吧 莫妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶回來的文件裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有寄給瑪奧博士的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士有個孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「決定把媽媽的耳環送給女兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算邁入宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的生活還是沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛而結合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生兒育女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後歌與文化被代代傳頌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐天下父母心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超時空網絡是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 凱茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離敵防空圈4萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全艦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信代號設定為「Sierra Bravo」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那些怪物身上吃夠了苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Frontier船團正面臨絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終於找到了蟲子的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須不惜一切代價全滅它們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求得生存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在敵人母星在數萬隻Vajra組成的防禦網保護下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰的最大目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破Vajra防禦網
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗中樞部女王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時讓主島降落行星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那顆行星成為我們新的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河妖精謝麗爾·諾姆的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引導我們走向勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位好運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去 馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也許不會高興吧 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我終究是天頂星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去心愛的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法默不做聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊部隊的維度吞噬者搭載情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在完成97%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我卑鄙也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非戰鬥人員移動前往主島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住衛星降落行星的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入所有能量與物資
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗原本就意味著滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顆行星是我們最後的開拓地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願宇宙的真理向我們微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間波的浪濤會穿越因果律與時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的歌聲如果會毀滅我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺死蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰應該已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這場戰鬥中活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 無法獨自飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了這道理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人遊戲到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在聽到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定都無法繼續唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部結束後 聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救出蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到的話 就聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回來 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住吧 這麼好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打著燈籠也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將抵達作戰宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始前TIME-60
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也沒有掛念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等燃盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有音樂和我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入敵人制空圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子的動靜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈陣速度是通常的1/3以下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現有組織行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效啊 這歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有搞頭 有搞頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇雪恨的日子到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會進入混戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆跟緊我屁股飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被擊中 涅涅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是臨陣磨槍的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見吧 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想侵犯這顆星球的人正大舉攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護這顆美麗的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親也一定希望這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正被分割孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁熱打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令主島降落地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織性在恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間波受到干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra軍戰鬥力增強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 蘭歌·李
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果真背叛了人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在繼續唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的網絡對蘭歌的歌起到增幅作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這首歌更合適的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的鑰匙在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的寶座已歸我所有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要置我們於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我妹妹遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓蘭歌做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們兄妹的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從侵略者手中保護Vajra生活的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你們先來襲擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先侵犯領土的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝吧 到銀河的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座1號中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是生命的閃光
